@Node Main "ARTM Anleitung"

                 @{u}ARTM   Amiga Real Time Monitor V2.04@{uu}


   @{b}ARTM@{ub}  displays and controls activities in your Amiga. It is full
supported by Intuition and it is very easy to use. It works under WB2.x
properly. You can change many system structures.



